{"tid":2479104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"碩鼠夜闖田灣邨單位　警員入屋助擒惜未果","createTime":"2021-04-07T14:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:12.000Z","uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3182af94aaffa0fe58aa932f842c04355946e2","tid":2479104,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情至今未止，港人抗疫疲勞飽受困擾，加上政府滅鼠不力導致鼠蹤處處，令市民擔憂鼠患夾擊下疫情更趨惡化。居住港島南區田灣邨一名姓劉住戶，向東網爆料指，今日(7日)凌晨1時許，在其田澤樓家中廚房驚現一隻身長逾6吋的大老鼠；劉將事件告知座頭姓吳(53歲)男保安，希望可透過吳向食環署求助，並安排滅鼠。<br />\n劉表示吳拒絕其要求，雙方更為此問題頓起爭執，劉報警求助。數名警員到田澤樓調查，並進入劉的單位廚房了解，據劉拍攝的短片顯示，在場一名警長取出強光電筒照射廚房內的暗角位置，未幾一隻約6吋長的老鼠從灶台狂奔向雪櫃後方，警長見狀，戴上手套並使用長柄晾衫叉，與此同時，其身旁的一名高級警員亦取出伸縮警棍，2人嘗試捉拿老鼠，惜最終無功而還。<br />\n劉在訪問中表示，感謝警方相助，並指田灣邨鼠患嚴重，不時目睹老鼠在走廊一帶亂竄，希望政府可以早日解決已困擾居民多時的鼠患問題。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210407/photo/bkn-20210407043332264-0407_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210407103511\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210407%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210407043332264-0407_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210407103511&h=213d19a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5ad5e58e8d13a8c71ac4cd35bc3f4ced860b0e9","tid":2479104,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210407/photo/bkn-20210407043332264-0407_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210407103511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210407%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210407043332264-0407_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210407103511&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=9afdd7e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210407/photo/bkn-20210407043332264-0407_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210407103511</a>"},{"pid":"8bf763365da3dd26257be75b2e18ed0688ff3b41","tid":2479104,"uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"碩鼠碩鼠 <br />\n無食我黍"},{"pid":"7ff2fcb643638ffcc80128aaece0a47b313dcb5e","tid":2479104,"uid":393733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:33:40.000Z","msg":"用伸縮警棍打老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射催淚彈啦on9"},{"pid":"460bef27781b05f0eeafd6b33a9991b53b44a128","tid":2479104,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\">與此同時，其身旁的一名高級警員亦取出伸縮警棍，2人嘗試捉拿老鼠，惜最終無功而還。</span>"},{"pid":"74488190170f70584a0923390af23de5348da95d","tid":2479104,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"黑警 facebook有冇出 post 話助民滅鼠？"},{"pid":"91d5398ec7c4eeb204dcaf380b4b380a0d5158fa","tid":2479104,"uid":123591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"警犬果然係弱智"},{"pid":"5b52d271b1d3342e19de8a2df50d9dbe78f16c07","tid":2479104,"uid":287422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"460bef27781b05f0eeafd6b33a9991b53b44a128","tid":2479104,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\">與此同時，其身旁的一名高級警員亦取出伸縮警棍，2人嘗試捉拿老鼠，惜最終無功而還。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc090c4efd5825e0605de78b6569d9732dc4cbe7","tid":2479104,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91d5398ec7c4eeb204dcaf380b4b380a0d5158fa","tid":2479104,"uid":123591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"警犬果然係弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"犬係捉唔唔到老鼠"},{"pid":"e6ea7b594970a44c2b7d3f31fec189106bb961dc","tid":2479104,"uid":168389,"like":4,"dislike"